Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\3c&HD831D9&\fad(450,450)\pos(1010,64)}-通向劇場之路-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES軍第13輸送部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要進行犯人押送 請求著陸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認緊急情況 許可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起了 做這樣惡趣味的偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在發源地秋葉星劇場觀看公演是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片天空的顏色到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇了心裡上壓抑的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓內心不被演藝迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家的眼神都那樣沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES那幫傢伙做了多麼惡劣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有WOTA入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡交戰就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認為粉紅色會很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 Kojiharu姐 很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小惠 還有76期的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Papa大廚 籌到食材了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些也可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的 含有豐富的維他命 還具有藥效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了小惠 可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再去弄點來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野生偶像 簡稱野偶的誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長 爭氣點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 身體還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 傷怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 只是頭痛得有點厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易來到秋葉星 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找醫生 認真治療一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星的人 憎恨著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為00拋棄了秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退是迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了優子 那個時候只有撤退一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是之後城市立即遭到了佔領
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DGTO的宣傳充斥了人們的雙耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短幾天居然開始洗腦宣傳了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能將天空的顏色傳達到網絡媒體上去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這裡到底是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是對於我們0048而言 極為神聖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時是連成員也禁止進入的聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從來了這裡之後就覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能聽到什麼聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼聲音在身體的深處迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin的Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 動作幅度再大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara完全沒閃耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話根本沒法讓雙晶素產生反應的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做得更好才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再強烈一些 迅速一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意識到手指的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣 再這樣一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣 像這樣動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是不甘心全交給成員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也想登場表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 現在的翼實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在已經做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 現在只能拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救秋葉星 拯救大家的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都看到了吧 那就是翼的Kirara的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連畢業已久的翼 都能讓Kirara發光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到這點 就需要超越願望 超越祈禱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強烈的思念!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些現役成員都做不到 還有何辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連翼這老太婆都豁出去拼命到這個地步了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老太婆?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 來拼一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別輸給老太婆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連咪醬都這麼毒舌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的熱情點燃了大家的心靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼醬 GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信她們的話就無從談起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把秋葉星奪回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最珍貴的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以實現的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使約定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以實現的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心懷著各種各樣的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢想卻相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成為0048
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夢想所鞭策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們乘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往秋葉星的 夢想列車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是 哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們 應該是在上排練課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到站了 不過這是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋葉星!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個 沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接納我們夢想的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和雙晶素產生反應了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定沒錯 有這種程度的反應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好真的能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 做得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙還沒有醒過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 凪沙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理是怎麼來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 我 一直在一片黑暗裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在原地不動的話 總覺得會被那片黑暗碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就開始跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定在那時可以忘記一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾見過這番景象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是不是有人在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧 還真有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不能再往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 第13代啊醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有第6代由依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有其他的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬她們在閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇場？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊醬就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是卻像咫尺天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優子她怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 剛才那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 你們看到的毫無疑問是AKB48劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB48開始於滅亡前的地球上的日本秋葉原的一個小劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡集合的少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏出了夢想的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 地球不是已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概不是真正的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是由強烈思念所形成的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 優子她並沒有到達那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕優子她還並沒有完全成為Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那個時候 優子放射出來的的確是Center Nova的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 而且也滿足了Center Nova的產生條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她沒有滿足Center Nova的消失條件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova的消失條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的絕對條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越時空的可怕的一體感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越時空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不單和成員 觀眾 工作人員還有會場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還同未來與過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法用語言表達的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一切融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得無處不在 無處可見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這帶有絲絲恐怖的心醉神迷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是優子的那消失方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻像是獨自一人躲進孤獨的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒時間了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演唱會會場在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請排隊等候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡真的合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合適 翼小姐來過聯繫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓Flying get闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在秋葉星被DES給重重包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本闖不進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信00等下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 奪回作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備超空間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙晶素同步裝置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara驅動器也沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便跳躍成功了 也不知道會到什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵就交給你來掌了 咪醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu Tomochin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也去會場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和演唱會那邊會合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先聖老師的傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 難道你聽得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 可並不是語言 而是身體直接感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次奪回秋葉星作戰的關鍵就在於
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME 無名的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細的我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒時間去想它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 去準備演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦闖了進去 就開始演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佔領了秋葉星的DGTO絕對會給DES增援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這之前 要把演唱會的氣氛炒到最熱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在藍花星上的演唱會 我發不出聲音的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幫了我 可我現在卻什麼忙都幫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和爸爸的封閉之門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為我所渴望的都在那道門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道如果一直被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就永遠無法打開那道門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我一定要成為Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵達那道門的門後面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也為了奪回秋葉星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家一起
