Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼萬一的話 就由我們來抵擋DES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳送門？難道是00？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去會撞上去 咪醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爺保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劇場女神們成功降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 我們回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有臉回來 你們這些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前明明那麼善良的秋葉星居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs30}滾回去 滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓緊的話 會被DES襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位想想特訓的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種場合說要齊心協力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星的人們…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏於人們內心深處的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也隨著演唱會調動起來 相互聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和雙晶素 假如能對此集體無意識產生反應的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了達到這點 觀眾們的感情十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅憑成員們的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使雙晶素產生反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論成員們怎麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法傳達給人們的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋葉星的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那麼善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的表情卻那麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能就此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾回去 滾回去…
