Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.40,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ひとつ拾って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.98,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}がむしゃらになって
