Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.51,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}流れ速くても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.99,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}怯えなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.18,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:40.56,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}そうだ 向こう岸はある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:49.13,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと 自分を信じろよ
