Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.04,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.31,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.91,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}寬廣無際的河流
