Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.18,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使距離遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:40.56,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也終將抵達彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:49.13,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}再對自己多些自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.09,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要對自己找藉口！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.70,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不試試看就不知道結果！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只能勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.89,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直 一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.46,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在自己定下的路上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.66,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.96,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水也在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.38,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那是汗水與淚水的河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.77,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.12,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使被激流捲走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.65,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要再試一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.85,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要說洩氣話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:39.00,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}牢牢抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:46.69,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}直到祈願實現的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.60,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}渡過河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:28.00,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつかの願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}土の中で眠って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:41.75,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}約束の時刻に 希望の根が出るんだ
