Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:50.79,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢など まだだめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.69,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どれくらい時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:00.16,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花は咲くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:05.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.94,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:15.51,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:20.15,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.62,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:28.26,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.36,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.70,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:28.00,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何時的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:41.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在約定好的時間 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}當兩人相遇之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:50.79,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢想還不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.69,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要過多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:00.16,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才會綻放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:05.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把這顆眼淚獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.94,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能夠更加閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:15.51,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我會從一直看著你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:20.15,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.62,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:28.26,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.36,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是輕輕撫慰空虛的你
